snippet.textDisplay: Epic! Epic! Epic! Coke Studio has hit the bullseye with this one! Epic song selection, perfect choice of singers, beautiful arrangement. Mulazim has got an impeccable voice. It's such a pleasure to hear him every time. And his rendition of 'Meri Hamjoliyan' is a treat to ears and soul. I won't accept anyone else covering the song since I have listened to it in his voice now. Fizza Javed holds great vocal prowess. And can we please take a moment to appreciate the work of the dholak guy, the brilliant Babar Khanna?!! He always manages to maintain sanctity of a song which requires perfect tabla or dholak work. This guy is mad genius and never once fails to take the songs like these to new heights with his master craftsman ship! A standing ovation to the whole team. Thank you for this!
